#cloud-config

### Ubuntu cloud-init config for user defaults ###
## Ref: https://cloudinit.readthedocs.io/
##
## Default user is `somni`, with password `somni`. You will be prompted to change the password.

hostname: somni-RPi-SenseStation
ssh_pwauth: true

groups:
- somni

users:
- name: somni
  gecos: somni
  primary_group: somni
  groups: sudo

chpasswd:
  expire: true
  list:
  - somni:somni

package_update: true
package_upgrade: true
